The requirements are as follows:
1.  Allows users to access contact database while on the organization network
2.  Allows more than one connections at a time
3.  Allows users to add, edit, and remove contacts
4.  Contacts must be able to be sorted alphabetically, via organization, country, and event
5.  Users can export an email formatted address list from selected contacts

Future requirements:
1.  Provide authenication process
2.  Host externally
3.  Allow uploading of business cards to accompany the database
4.  Provide a map where you can select a country and all the contacts from that country are selected
